The '''Blan Forests''' was a series of [[Forest/Legends|forests]] located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Brosi]] in the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]]. During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], [[Corporate Sector Authority/Legends|Corporate Sector Authority]] [[Supervisor (Corporate Sector Authority)|Supervisor]] [[Wasith]] hired several [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]] to flush out and eradicate the [[Brosin Underground]] from the Blan Forests but they were unsuccessful in doing so.<ref name="Alliance Intelligence Reports">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

